          <li>Update to elementary runtime 7</li>
          <li>Updated translations</li>
        </ul>
      </description>
    </release>
    <release version="2.4.1" date="2022-01-24" urgency="medium">
      <description>
        <ul>
          <li>Update to elementary runtime 6.1</li>
